---
import KvBanner from './KvBanner.astro';
---

<section id="partners" class="pt-0">
  <KvBanner color="green" title="Partners" />
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 overlap-wrap pb-16" data-parallax="16">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        
        <!-- Temasek Foundation -->
        <div class="colorful-card p-6" data-shimmer>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start h-24 mb-3">
            <img 
              src="/assets/logo_tf.svg" 
              alt="Temasek Foundation logo" 
              class="h-12 w-auto object-contain reveal" 
              loading="lazy" 
              decoding="async" 
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Temasek Foundation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">
            Temasek Foundation supports a diverse range of programmes that uplift lives and communities in Asia, including Singapore.<br/>
            Made possible through philanthropic endowments gifted by Temasek, an investment company headquartered in Singapore, Temasek Foundation’s programmes strive towards achieving positive outcomes for individuals and communities now, and for generations to come.<br/>
            Collectively, Temasek Foundation’s programmes strengthen social resilience, foster international exchange and regional capabilities, advance science, and protect the planet.
          </p>
          <span class="text-sm mt-2">For more information, visit: </span><a href="https://www.temasekfoundation.org.sg" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline text-sm inline-block" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.temasekfoundation.org.sg</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 5P Global Movement -->
        <div class="colorful-card p-6" data-shimmer>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start h-24 mb-3">
            <img 
              src="/assets/5P-LOGO.svg" 
              alt="5P Global Movement logo" 
              class="h-24 w-auto object-contain reveal" 
              loading="lazy" 
              decoding="async" 
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold">5P Global Movement</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">
            The 5P Global Movement is a non-profit organisation which promotes harmony in diversity through incorporating the 5P (peace, prosperity, people, planet, partnership) values in all its programmes.
          </p>
          <span class="text-sm mt-2">For more information, visit: </span><a href="https://5pglobal.org" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline text-sm inline-block" target="_blank" rel="noopener">5pglobal.org</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
